THIS BLOCK IS NO LONGER SUPPORTED. PLEASE USE THE KINECT COMMON BRIDGE
https://github.com/wieden-kennedy/Cinder-KCB

-----------------------------------------

This block wraps Microsoft official SDK for the Kinect 
device.

The "ContoursApp" sample requires "Cinder-OpenCV":
https://github.com/cinder/Cinder-OpenCV

Installation instructions, changelog, and more information here:
http://www.bantherewind.com/kinectsdk-for-cinder

-----------------------------------------

